  schema:name "Dark Forest: Pioneering On-Chain Gaming with Zero-Knowledge Proofs" ;
  schema:description "Analysis of Dark Forest, the first real-time strategy game running on Ethereum, and its cryptographic fog of war system using zkSNARKs. How zero-knowledge proofs enable private state in public blockchains, and how this influenced autonomous world design." ;
